{"id":"ISS-20260609-031","title":"Exposed rc6 gate is stale against current hook/config files","status":"completed","priority":3,"severity":"medium","source":"discover","description":"The root package still exposes `pnpm rc6:gate`, but the gate re-runs a stale rc5 anchor and checks current files against outdated assumptions. With build/tests skipped, it fails on rc5 legacy checks, missing Cursor SessionStart/PreToolUse slots, and a deleted `packages/cli/src/commands/hooks.ts` path before it can provide a useful release signal. This makes the named gate misleading and likely to be bypassed rather than trusted.","fix_direction":"Either retire rc5:gate/rc6:gate from package.json, or update rc6 checks to current hook config ownership and command files, then add a lightweight test/CI assertion that exposed gate scripts execute successfully with FABRIC_GATE_SKIP_BUILD=1 and FABRIC_GATE_SKIP_TESTS=1.","context":{"location":"scripts/rc6-coverage-gate.mjs:439","suggested_fix":"","notes":"Discovered by prompt inconsistency sweep DBP-20260609-023700"},"tags":["test-gate-drift","release-gate","stale-script"],"affected_components":["package.json rc6:gate","scripts/rc6-coverage-gate.mjs","scripts/rc5-coverage-gate.mjs","hook config release checks"],"feedback":[],"issue_history":[{"from":null,"to":"registered","actor":"discovery-agent","at":"2026-06-08T18:50:37.990Z","note":"Discovered by prompt inconsistency sweep DBP-20260609-023700"},{"from":"registered","to":"completed","actor":"user","at":"2026-07-05T03:13:55.401Z","note":"Closed: rc5/rc6 (and rc2-rc4) coverage-gate scripts retired; superseded by release-rc skill."}],"created_at":"2026-06-08T18:50:37.990Z","updated_at":"2026-07-05T03:13:55.401Z","resolved_at":"2026-07-05T03:13:55.401Z","resolution":"Retired the per-rc coverage-gate pattern: deleted scripts/rc2..rc6-coverage-gate.mjs (all 5), removed rc5:gate + rc6:gate from root package.json scripts, un-pinned rc6:gate from scripts/test-strategy-gate.mjs required-scripts list, and updated docs/TESTING.md (Commands list + Scenario Matrix Release-drift-gate row now point to the release-rc skill). The per-rc gate pattern died at rc6 and was superseded by the release-rc skill; matches the issue fix_direction. Migrate-before-delete node sweep (KT-PIT-0035) confirmed no live references remained (only .workflow/ historical artifacts, which do not count). pnpm test:strategy PASS and pnpm lint (knip --strict) clean post-change."}
